data.description: Beautifully maintained Smart wired Home with lots of upgrades. Gourmet Kitchen package includes Granite Counters, Double Oven, Large Island, and 36'' Upper cabinets. Loft has been enclosed to make a 5th Bedroom, Office or Playroom. Living Room has Custom Built in Niches with Stone Surround, Electric Fireplace and 60'' Flat Screen TV. !st Floor also has Office/Study. Large Master Bedroom features Barn Door leading into Master Bath that has both Shower, Large Bathtub and Walk in Closet. 1st Floor has Office/Study. Home has additional built in shelving in Garage and in Closet under Stairwell for extra Storage. Custom Wrought Iron Security doors on Front Entrance and Rear Sliding Glass Doors(with doggie opening). Backyard has Shady Ramada, Custom Pavers form the Patio and Walkways out to Lawn Fenced Dog Run with soft gravel for your pets. Sides of Backyard feature Plant Beds and Planters to fill with your favorite Plants or Trees. Close to DM, Raytheon and Amazon.
